  "title": "Electrical Construction Supervisor and Driver",
  "description": "<p>Teh Engineering is an established local electrical engineering firm that believes in producing work that we are proud of. Being a family-oriented company, we believe in taking care of our employees and to work harmoniously together as a team.</p><p>We are now looking for a Site Supervisor to join our team!<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise and coordinate manpower schedule for project completion</li><li>Liaise and coordinate with clients and other contractors on work progress and variation orders.</li><li>Update electrical drawings and single line drawings</li><li>Manage team of construction workers</li><li>Resolve site issues</li><li>Ferry team of workers around</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Holds a Class 3 Driving Licence and is familiar with Singapore roads</li><li>Have relevant electrical engineering qualifications (Minimum ITE Certificate, and above)</li><li>8 years of relevant experience in M&E construction industry</li><li>Able to work in fast-paced environment and handle tight deadlines</li><li>Proactive and Self-driven</li></ul><p></p>",
